item_name.value: Advil Pain Reliever and Fever Reducer, Pain Relief Medicine with Ibuprofen 200mg for Headache, Backache, Menstrual Pain and Joint Pain Relief - 50x2 Coated Tablets

directions.value: Directions: do not take more than directed. The smallest effective dose should be used. Adults and children 12 years and over: take 1 caplet every 4 to 6 hours while symptoms persist. If pain or fever does not respond to 1 caplet, 2 caplets may be used. Do not exceed 6 caplets in 24 hours, unless directed by a doctor. Children under 12 years: ask a doctor. Other information: read all warnings and directions before use. Keep carton stored at 20-25 degrees C (68-77 degrees F). Avoid excessive heat above 40 degrees C (104 degrees F)

model_name.value: Advil Pain Reliever Single Dose Packets

safety_warning.value: Do not use if seal under bottle cap imprinted with "Sealed for your protection" is broken or missing. Ibuprofen may cause a severe allergic reaction, especially in people allergic to aspirin. Symptoms may include: Hives, Facial Swelling, Asthma (wheezing), Shock, Skin reddening, Rash, Blisters. If an allergic reaction occurs, stop use and seek medical help right away. Stomach bleeding warning: This product contains an NSAID, which may cause severe stomach bleeding. Please read packaging before use for full list of Warnings.

title.text: Advil Pain Medication Ibuprofen 200mg Tablets, Headache Pain Relief, 100 Coated Tablets in 50 Single-Dose Packets for Adults and Children 12+

bullets.text: Single-dose packets support convenient and hygienic pain relief, making them ideal for travel, events, or sharing with guests. Each packet contains two coated tablets, allowing for easy portability and minimized contact, so you can keep relief accessible in purses, backpacks, or office drawers without carrying a full bottle.

Versatile formula is designed to relieve a wide range of common pains, including headaches, backaches, menstrual pain, joint pain, toothaches, arthritis, muscle pain, and fever. Suitable for adults and children 12 years and over, this product helps you manage everyday discomforts with one trusted solution.

Adding an easy-open cap or arthritis-friendly packaging option would benefit users with limited hand mobility, making access to pain relief more manageable. Considering enhanced packaging can help support a wider range of user needs and improve overall experience.

Coated tablets are designed for easier swallowing, making pain relief more comfortable for those who may have difficulty with uncoated pills. Smooth coating helps tablets glide down, supporting a more pleasant experience when taking your pain reliever.

Active ingredient is clearly listed as ibuprofen 200mg (NSAID), offering trusted over-the-counter pain and fever relief. The formulation is intended for effective results and transparent labeling, so you know exactly what you are taking with every dose.

description.text:
This ibuprofen-based pain medication is formulated to provide effective relief from a variety of common discomforts, including headache pain, backaches, menstrual pain, joint and muscle aches, toothaches, and symptoms associated with arthritis and colds. Each tablet contains 200mg of ibuprofen, a nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory ingredient widely used by adults and children 12 years and older for dependable, everyday support.

Conveniently packaged in 50 individual packets, with two coated tablets per packet, this product is ideal for those who need pain meds on the go. The single-dose packets fit easily into purses, backpacks, or desk drawers, making them a practical option for travel, work, or sharing with others in communal settings. The coating on each tablet is designed to help make swallowing more comfortable, especially for individuals who find uncoated pills difficult to take.

This unscented, over-the-counter option is easy to store within the recommended temperature range, and the long shelf life means you can keep it in your home, office, or car for when discomfort strikes. The clear labeling of each packet ensures you always know what you are taking, supporting informed decisions about managing pain and fever when you need reliable support.

Content.title: Advil Pain Medication Ibuprofen 200mg Tablets, Headache Pain Relief, 100 Coated Tablets in 50 Single-Dose Packets for Adults and Children 12+
Content.description:
This ibuprofen-based pain medication is formulated to provide effective relief from a variety of common discomforts, including headache pain, backaches, menstrual pain, joint and muscle aches, toothaches, and symptoms associated with arthritis and colds. Each tablet contains 200mg of ibuprofen, a nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory ingredient widely used by adults and children 12 years and older for dependable, everyday support.

Conveniently packaged in 50 individual packets, with two coated tablets per packet, this product is ideal for those who need pain meds on the go. The single-dose packets fit easily into purses, backpacks, or desk drawers, making them a practical option for travel, work, or sharing with others in communal settings. The coating on each tablet is designed to help make swallowing more comfortable, especially for individuals who find uncoated pills difficult to take.

This unscented, over-the-counter option is easy to store within the recommended temperature range, and the long shelf life means you can keep it in your home, office, or car for when discomfort strikes. The clear labeling of each packet ensures you always know what you are taking, supporting informed decisions about managing pain and fever when you need reliable support.
bullet_points: Single-dose packets support convenient and hygienic pain relief, making them ideal for travel, events, or sharing with guests. Each packet contains two coated tablets, allowing for easy portability and minimized contact, so you can keep relief accessible in purses, backpacks, or office drawers without carrying a full bottle.

Versatile formula is designed to relieve a wide range of common pains, including headaches, backaches, menstrual pain, joint pain, toothaches, arthritis, muscle pain, and fever. Suitable for adults and children 12 years and over, this product helps you manage everyday discomforts with one trusted solution.

Adding an easy-open cap or arthritis-friendly packaging option would benefit users with limited hand mobility, making access to pain relief more manageable. Considering enhanced packaging can help support a wider range of user needs and improve overall experience.

Coated tablets are designed for easier swallowing, making pain relief more comfortable for those who may have difficulty with uncoated pills. Smooth coating helps tablets glide down, supporting a more pleasant experience when taking your pain reliever.

Active ingredient is clearly listed as ibuprofen 200mg (NSAID), offering trusted over-the-counter pain and fever relief. The formulation is intended for effective results and transparent labeling, so you know exactly what you are taking with every dose.
